dct_description_sm: This raster dataset is a Landsat map of Hungary. Source of landsat layer is NASA Landsat TM database. Database update follows the updates of source data. The resolution is set to improve with updates, current resolution is 28,5 m/pixel.  The colors on the landsat picture: blue-rivers, lakes; green – forests; different brows or yellows – cultivated lands .
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
